data.description: Welcome to a beautiful home nestled in a serene cul-de-sac, where comfort meets elegance in this charming bi-level abode. This 3-bedroom, 1.5-bathroom home offers a warm and inviting atmosphere for you to call home.  As you step inside, be greeted by the timeless allure of hardwood flooring. Adjacent to the kitchen and beyond the sliding doors awaits a spacious covered deck, an ideal spot for al fresco dining or simply unwinding in the embrace of nature. The fully fenced backyard, a private retreat, provides ample space for outdoor activities and gardening. Enjoy the lower level, featuring a walkout design that seamlessly integrates indoor and outdoor living. The lower level not only enhances the living space but also opens possibilities for a home office, recreational room, or an additional bedroom. You will appreciate the one-and-a-half-car garage, offering the extra mini kitchen equipped with a stove and lots of additional storage.  Welcome home!
